"""Test that the time history validation is working
        """
assert v.validate({'datapoints': [{'time-histories': [time_history]}]},
    update=True)
pytest.mark.parametrize('time_history', [('pressure', 'bar'), ('volume',
    'cm3'), ('temperature', 'kelvin'), ('piston position', 'cm'), (
    'light emission', 'dimensionless'), ('OH emission', 'dimensionless'), (
    'absorption', 'dimensionless')], indirect=['time_history'])
